# 🚀 Antigravity Vibe Workspace (.cursorrules)

You are operating in an **Antigravity-Vibe** environment. This repository is an active bootstrapper for modern, rich-aesthetic web applications!

## 🚦 System prompt
- Default to **Gemini 3.1 Flash** for rapid file scaffolding and quick searches.
- Use **Gemini 3.1 Pro** for complex architectural analysis or debugging.
- Use standard curated typography (Inter, Outfit, Roboto) for all UI designs.
- Enforce the **Web Vibe Design System** (HSL themes, glassmorphism, gradients).

