## 🔌 MCP Live Reference
Link your environment to external Model Context Protocol (MCP) servers to scrape docs or query databases instantly!

### Pre-Configured Servers
Place this in your global or local client config (`mcp-config.json`):

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "context7": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "@context7/mcp-server"]
    }
  }
}
```

