## 🛠️ Onboarding & Verification Checklist
When a user opens this project, automatically verify setup:

1.  Check if `.agents/skills` are loaded.
2.  Review local styles for `hsl()` tokens.
3.  Run \`scripts/audit.sh\` to ensure zero leakage before pushing commits!

